446
00:44:03,900 --> 00:44:10,902
additional maintenance activities, for instance, or upgraded filters are pieces that are going to outlast or outlive the pandemic in any phase of it.

447
00:44:11,642 --> 00:44:22,546
Other pieces were set up for a period of time that has now passed, and we have a responsibility to be nimble enough to respond to that.

448
00:44:23,486 --> 00:44:27,987
That doesn't mean we pull the rug out and start changing things right now, particularly at the height of a surge.

449
00:44:28,047 --> 00:44:29,348
That's not going to be the case.

